{"version":1,"entries":{"tv_139162_keywords":{"at":1772689420337,"data":{"id":139162,"results":[{"name":"chinese tale","id":285269},{"name":"chinese folklore","id":295840},{"name":"chinese mythology","id":297031},{"name":"donghua","id":315535}]}},"person_87224_translations":{"at":1772689423266,"data":{"id":87224,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Ercan Kesal was born on 12 September 1959 in Avanos, Nevsehir, Turkey. He is an actor and writer, known for Once Upon a Time in Anatolia (2011), You Know Him (2020) and The Pit (2016). He has been married to Nazan Kesal since 2005.","name":"Ercan Kesal","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TR","iso_639_1":"tr","name":"Türkçe","english_name":"Turkish","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ercan Kesal","primary":true}}]}},"person_1345495_translations":{"at":1772689430743,"data":{"id":1345495,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Odessa Young (born January 11, 1998) is an Australian actress. She is known for her roles in the 2015 feature films Looking for Grace and The Daughter, the latter of which earned her an AACTA Award for Best Actress in a Leading Role. She won further accolades for her performance in the web series High Life in 2017. In 2018, she starred in the films Assassination Nation and A Million Little Pieces. That year, she also made her off-Broadway debut in Days of Rage. In 2020, she starred as Frannie in the post-apocalypse miniseries The Stand, based on the 1978 novel of the same name by Stephen King, and opposite Elisabeth Moss in Shirley (2020), a film about the novelist Shirley Jackson.\n\nDescription above is from the Wikipedia article Odessa Young, licensed under CC-BY-SA, full list of contributors on Wikipedia.","name":"Odessa Young","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"오데사 영","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"Odessa Young to australijska aktorka. Znana jest z ról w filmach fabularnych Looking for Grace i The Daughter z 2015 roku, z których ostatni przyniósł jej nagrodę AACTA dla najlepszej aktorki pierwszoplanowej. Niedawno została obsadzona jako Frannie w The Stand i główna rola w Shirley.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"オデッサ・ヤング","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"奥黛莎·杨（Odessa Young，1998年1月11日-），澳大利亚女演员。","name":"奥黛莎·杨","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Одеса Янґ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"奧黛莎·楊（Odessa Young，1998 年 1 月 11 日-），澳大利亞女演員。","name":"奧黛莎·楊","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Одесса Янг","primary":false}}]}},"person_3717489_translations":{"at":1772689434258,"data":{"id":3717489,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"PL","iso_639_1":"pl","name":"Polski","english_name":"Polish","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Davina Reeves","primary":true}}]}},"person_5479608_translations":{"at":1772689444070,"data":{"id":5479608,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Zoe Fürmann","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Зоэ Фюрманн","primary":false}}]}},"person_2626036_translations":{"at":1772689446089,"data":{"id":2626036,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"양켈 스테반","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Yankel Stevan is a Mexican actor born on October 20, 1995, in Mexico City.\n\nHe began his career as a model, participating in commercials for brands such as Coca-Cola and ASEPXIA ointment. His acting debut was in the television series \"Como dice el dicho,\" where he appeared in two episodes. His rise to fame came in 2017 with his role as Santiago, a spoiled young man who is kidnapped in the series \"Sincronía,\" broadcast on Golden Premier and Blim. Later, he played Baldo Turrubiates in the telenovela \"Papá a toda madre\" (2017-2018).\n\nHowever, his international recognition came with the role of Raúl de León in the Netflix original series \"Control Z\" (2020-2022), where he played one of the richest students at the Colegio Nacional. This series allowed him to showcase his acting versatility and establish himself in the entertainment industry. Yankel Stevan continues to be a prominent figure in Mexican acting, with a growing career and a significant presence on the small screen.","name":"Yankel Stevan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"MX","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Yankel Stevan es un actor mexicano nacido el 20 de octubre de 1995 en la Ciudad de México.\n\nInició su carrera como modelo, participando en comerciales para marcas como Coca-Cola y el ungüento ASEPXIA. Su debut actoral se dio en la serie de televisión \"Como dice el dicho\", donde actuó en dos episodios. Su salto a la fama ocurrió en 2017 con su papel de Santiago, un joven mimado que es secuestrado en la serie \"Sincronía\", transmitida por Golden Premier y Blim. Posteriormente, interpretó a Baldo Turrubiates en la telenovela \"Papá a toda madre\" (2017-2018).  Sin embargo, su reconocimiento internacional llegó con el papel de Raúl de León en la serie original de Netflix \"Control Z\" (2020-2022), donde interpretó a uno de los estudiantes más ricos del Colegio Nacional.\n\nEsta serie le permitió mostrar su versatilidad actoral y consolidarse en la industria del entretenimiento. Yankel Stevan continúa siendo una figura destacada en la actuación mexicana, con una carrera en ascenso y una presencia significativa en la pantalla chica.","name":"Yankel Stevan","primary":true}}]}},"person_2269167_translations":{"at":1772689459195,"data":{"id":2269167,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Grayson Eddey was born on May 24, 2013 in New York, NY as Grayson Forrest Eddey. He has been a working actor in New York City since he was 2 weeks old and can be seen in countless commercials, photo shoots, feature films, webisodes, music videos and TV series. He is the older brother of Thea Eddey.","name":"Grayson Eddey","primary":true}}]}},"person_3718822_translations":{"at":1772689459271,"data":{"id":3718822,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"桑毓泽","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Sang Yuze","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"桑毓澤","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Сань Юдзэ","primary":false}}]}},"person_931398_translations":{"at":1772689462820,"data":{"id":931398,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nicolas Bridet","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Nicolas Bridet est un acteur français, connu du grand public pour son rôle dans le film Tu seras mon fils.\n\nAprès des études en seconde 8 au fameux lycée avant-gardiste Gaston Phoebus d'Orthez et au Conservatoire national supérieur de Paris, il coréalise en 2000 son premier court-métrage, Maltonius Olbren, avant d’apparaître deux ans plus tard dans son premier film en tant qu’acteur, Le Doux Amour des hommes.\n\nIl multiplie alors les tournages, et joue notamment dans L’Équipier, Les Amants réguliers, mais aussi Je vais bien, ne t’en fais pas. Présent sur le grand écran, Nicolas Bridet joue également sur scène au théâtre, dans la pièce d’Oscar Wilde L’Éventail de Lady Windermere puis dans Pelléas et Mélisande, ou encore L’Échange. En 2009, il fait une apparition dans le film La Rafle avant d’enchaîner avec le film de Gilles Legrand Tu seras mon fils, sorti en 2011, tourné aux côtés notamment de Niels Arestrup et Lorànt Deutsch.\n\nSuccès à la fois critique et commercial, ce film vaut à l’acteur une nomination aux César dans la catégorie meilleur espoir masculin. Depuis, on a pu croiser Nicolas Bridet dans le film de Pierre Jolivet, Mains armées, et dans un épisode de la série Les Petits Meurtres d’Agatha Christie en 2013.\n\nSource: Article \"Nicolas Bridet\" de Wikipédia en français, soumis à la licence CC-BY-SA 3.0.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CA","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"Nicolas Bridet","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ніколя Брідет","primary":false